  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4953319">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4953319/" class="title-link">煤老板自述三十年</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4953319"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4869189/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4869189-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4869189/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">E＝mc^2</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-05-18"
      class="main-meta">2011-05-18 13:19:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4953319_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  类似于戏说的煤老板们人生酸甜苦辣，可其中的辛酸和努力只有当事人或者类似的经历的才能体会。这些老的和新生代的煤老板也需要大智慧。有中国人传统的狡黠也有中国人传统的乡土美德。 书的最后用《了凡四训》结尾。结尾结的很出色。就像佛教里说的圆满。或者说是功德。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4953319/#comments">(1回应)</a>
